<item>
            <title>[WICKET-4559] Component#getMarkupId() generates id that gets hidden by AdBlock</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/WICKET-4559</link>
                <project id="12310561" key="WICKET">Wicket</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Component#getMarkupId() generates ids containing string &quot;ad&quot;. Element with such id (e.g., &quot;buttonad&quot;) is then hidden by the AdBlock plugin (because it matches AdBlock&apos;s CSS selector #buttonad).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Since AdBlock is quite a common plugin, this issue might affect most of the applications using Wicket.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Test project and screenshot is attached.&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;#8211;&lt;br/&gt;
Wicket 1.4.21&lt;br/&gt;
Firefox 12, AdBlock 2.0.3&lt;br/&gt;
Linux 3.3.5, x86_64&lt;/p&gt;</description>
